Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.10,0:01:01.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪的梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.52,0:01:09.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我名叫岩谷尚文比普通人宅一些的大学二年级学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.40,0:01:15.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好刺眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.86,0:01:22.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要说我为家里做过什么那就只有拯救了差点失足的弟弟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.70,0:01:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在自己家生活还能拿到零用钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.50,0:01:30.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要去打工享受着宅的生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.43,0:01:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话虽如此我绝不是一个家里蹲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.26,0:01:46.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没钱的时候会在图书馆淘轻小说看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.10,0:01:50.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是这种没有出奇之处非常平凡的阿宅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.65,0:01:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.23,0:01:55.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.95,0:01:58.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到捡起这本书
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.62,0:02:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四圣武器书?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带来终末灾厄的浪潮?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.71,0:02:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后为了拯救世界召唤异世界的四位勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.17,0:02:14.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是轻小说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.92,0:02:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四位勇者分别以剑、枪、弓、盾为武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.05,0:02:25.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不盾不是武器而是防具吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.14,0:02:28.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说女主角根本没出场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.81,0:02:31.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位公主也有点婊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.32,0:02:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每位勇者都有优点挺帅的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.44,0:02:39.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是四主角的故事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.03,0:02:43.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剑、枪、弓然后盾也有故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.93,0:03:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.18,0:03:06.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.14,0:03:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人请救救这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.10,0:03:11.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.52,0:03:14.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.57,0:03:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来这里是什么地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.15,0:03:21.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.71,0:03:44.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人请救救这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.09,0:03:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.05,0:03:53.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况非常复杂…我们使用古代仪式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.97,0:03:58.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将几位传说中的四圣勇者召唤来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.52,0:04:02.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四圣?那我们四个是传说中的勇者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.27,0:04:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界正面临灭亡的危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.82,0:04:11.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人们恳请各位帮帮我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果只是听听的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.95,0:04:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.16,0:04:17.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.83,0:04:21.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能让我们回原来的世界吗不然免谈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.21,0:04:26.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们对于强制将人召唤来这事没有一点罪恶感吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.25,0:04:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算世界和平了如果一下子回到原来的世界就等于做白工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.76,0:04:35.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会在什么程度上考虑我们的想法?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.30,0:04:40.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据情况我们也可以与你们为敌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.02,0:04:44.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们几个不仅明白了现在的状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.44,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至还开始主张立场要求报酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.31,0:04:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先请几位见见我国的梅洛马格王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.99,0:04:56.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到时候再谈酬金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.16,0:04:58.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来还有考虑的余地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.50,0:05:05.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管和谁谈都一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.46,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是有多可靠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.01,0:05:15.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的来到异世界了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.43,0:05:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.01,0:05:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服的风像国外旅行手册上写的那样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道你没有离开过日本吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.90,0:05:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果要用国外的风作比较这里和地中海地区的气候差不多吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.19,0:05:36.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦真抱歉我没知识也没表达能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.25,0:05:48.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几位就是古代传说中的四圣勇者吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.67,0:05:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是梅洛马格的王奥托克雷·梅洛马格三十二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.97,0:05:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者们报上你们各自的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.39,0:06:02.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天木炼年龄是16岁高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.68,0:06:06.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是北村元康21岁大学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.48,0:06:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是我呢川澄树17岁高中生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.11,0:06:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最后就是我我是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.15,0:06:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼和元康还有树吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.66,0:06:20.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王你忘记我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.83,0:06:23.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.66,0:06:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然叫「国王」不行哦要有敬意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.92,0:06:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那叫陛下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.71,0:06:30.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是太严肃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫国王就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.92,0:06:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随便了我叫岩谷尚文20岁大学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.93,0:06:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了首先必须说明情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.93,0:06:47.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无视我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.27,0:06:53.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我国梅洛马格还有这个世界正面临毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.98,0:06:58.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然他的态度让我不爽不过他的话总结一下就是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.53,0:07:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个世界有终末预言这种东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.20,0:07:09.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预言说导致世界毁灭的「浪潮」会数次到访
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.54,0:07:15.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不击退浪潮散播的灾厄世界就会毁灭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.80,0:07:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各国自古就拥有名叫「龙刻沙漏」的道具
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.51,0:07:24.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凭它可以知道浪潮来袭的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.31,0:07:29.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我们被召唤前第一波浪潮袭击了这个国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.35,0:07:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该国的骑士与冒险者勉强击退了最初的浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.53,0:07:40.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是第二、第三波浪潮会更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.20,0:07:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到浪潮不再来袭沙漏的沙才会停止下落
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.70,0:07:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,距离第二波还有不到一个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们太小看浪潮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.75,0:07:56.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过实际体验过后深切地感受到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.38,0:08:01.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是只有四圣勇者能够对抗的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.47,0:08:04.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且按照传承召唤了你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.89,0:08:07.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在情况万分火急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.97,0:08:11.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不就和刚才那本书上看到的剧情一样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.65,0:08:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.36,0:08:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么把我们召唤来应该不会不给报酬吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.36,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白然如果顺利击退浪潮我们会支付足够的报醐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.66,0:08:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们肯承诺就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.95,0:08:31.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要不与我为敌我会协助你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.62,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但别以为我会服从你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.92,0:08:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对可别小瞧我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.17,0:08:38.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.92,0:08:42.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些家伙一直高高在上啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.55,0:08:44.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来事情有定论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.34,0:08:48.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者们啊确认你们的状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.97,0:08:50.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,状态是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.72,0:08:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.06,0:08:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么搞的刚到这个世界的时候就应该注意到吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.23,0:09:00.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么知道你这一脸「我是情报通」的表情怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.07,0:09:03.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,视线的边缘有没有图标?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对着它集中精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.29,0:09:13.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.13,0:09:17.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,LV1吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.54,0:09:19.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.00,0:09:23.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊这样下去都不知道能不能战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.84,0:09:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说这是怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.80,0:09:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名为状态的魔法只有勇者可以使用的能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.68,0:09:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们该怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.06,0:09:38.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始踏上冒险旅途培养各位所拥有的传说武器进行强化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.77,0:09:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一上来就厉害的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.73,0:09:44.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说我的连武器都不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.90,0:09:48.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说武器派上用场前使用其他武器不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.99,0:09:52.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这一点之后再讨论吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.70,0:09:55.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之我们应该先磨炼自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.12,0:09:58.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尽全力提高等级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们四个人组成队伍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.59,0:10:03.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.51,0:10:09.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人们需要分别招募同伴进行冒险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.60,0:10:10.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.43,0:10:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据传说传说武器有着互相排斥的特性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.23,0:10:21.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,·起行动会阻碍成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.19,0:10:23.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.11,0:10:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说武器似乎把对话和信息转换成日语了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.57,0:10:34.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天快要黑了今天好好休息明天再启程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.95,0:10:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会准备优秀的冒险者给诸位当同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.58,0:10:44.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经为各位备好了房间这边请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.80,0:10:47.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四圣勇者似乎被召唤来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:47.72,0:10:49.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家召唤了所有勇者?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.68,0:10:50.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.14,0:10:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么盾之勇者也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.68,0:11:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,传说的勇者待遇果然好带路的女孩子也可爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.94,0:11:04.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,端上来的料理虽然味道不可思议但也豪华
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.69,0:11:07.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说这好像游戏呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.70,0:11:11.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不就是游戏吗和 Emerald Online一模一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.37,0:11:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么游戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.54,0:11:15.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超有名的好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.29,0:11:17.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.00,0:11:21.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是网游是主机游戏的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.75,0:11:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叫 Dimension Wave
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.50,0:11:25.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对吧是VRMM0
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.30,0:11:28.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以说几乎和 Prabe Star Online一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.22,0:11:31.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来整理一下信息吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.84,0:11:35.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炼你说的VRMM0不代表其他意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.72,0:11:38.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也明白这是什么意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像在SF游戏里出现过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.31,0:11:44.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记得在轻小说里看过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.44,0:11:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一确认一下常识1000日币上画的人是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.86,0:11:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,汤田正人-谷和原刚太郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.91,0:11:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.12,0:11:56.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年的流行语大奖是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢的声优是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第二次世界大战的获胜国是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.20,0:12:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总理大臣叫什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.29,0:12:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们来自于不同的日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:07.17,0:12:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是至少我不认为是同一个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.59,0:12:14.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么异世界的日本真实存在吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.60,0:12:18.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为只是时代不同没想到差距居然这么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.85,0:12:23.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了大家都玩过和这个世界一样的游戏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.85,0:12:25.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么只有我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.65,0:12:28.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦什么嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.48,0:12:31.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不我就觉得果然是因为盾…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也这么想?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.66,0:12:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.78,0:12:38.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦怎么了盾有什么不对嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.16,0:12:43.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好元康哥哥在常识范围内告诉你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.42,0:12:48.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我的认知中 Shi lder就是以盾为主的职业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.71,0:12:52.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不存在高等级玩家的输家职业
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NO
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.97,0:13:00.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和他一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.06,0:13:07.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地形之类的怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.48,0:13:10.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我知道的地形几乎一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.11,0:13:18.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧我弱小的话只要依靠同伴不就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.74,0:13:21.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许里面还有女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.12,0:13:28.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾给人防御敌人的攻击守护同伴的印象吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.09,0:13:33.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在原来的世界不受欢迎说不定会在这里发生一场邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.72,0:13:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题难得来到异世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.14,0:13:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪怕我弱小也会有办法的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.27,0:13:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好要加油了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.60,0:13:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊明天就是冒险的开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.15,0:13:50.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天就回房间赶紧睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.15,0:13:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有澡堂什么的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.94,0:13:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很可能是木桶哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.90,0:13:58.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错明天我的大冒险就要开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.05,0:14:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们召集了一批有志与传说中的勇者一起对抗浪潮的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.89,0:14:26.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人会成为我们的同伴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.06,0:14:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有可爱的女孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.44,0:14:36.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来的英雄们啊启程吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.74,0:14:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦由他们来选吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.21,0:14:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三人五人四人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.55,0:14:53.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.30,0:14:58.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连我都没想到会发生这种情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.47,0:15:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然无人愿意跟随完全没有人望啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.06,0:15:05.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种传闻都传开了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.98,0:15:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生了什么吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.85,0:15:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实城里在传盾之勇者对这个世界不熟悉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.19,0:15:20.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据传说勇者能理解这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.57,0:15:23.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家在说你好像不满足这个条件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.87,0:15:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.70,0:15:27.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是昨晚的闲聊被人偷听了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.00,0:15:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.50,0:15:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就凭这个?我的确是不熟悉啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.84,0:15:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说炼你有五个人了分我一个啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.17,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌拉帮结派会抛下跟不上的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.97,0:15:45.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元康你怎么看这是不是很过分?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.18,0:15:49.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀这也不能算是很过分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然不完全否定吗窝火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.23,0:15:55.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然平均地每个人分三人比较好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.61,0:15:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但强行分配会影响士气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.24,0:16:01.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就要我独自启程吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.57,0:16:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是盾啊在你们的理论中属于输家的武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.95,0:16:09.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有同伴要怎么变强啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.79,0:16:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.30,0:16:18.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这女孩是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.80,0:16:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以跟着盾之勇者大人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.26,0:16:24.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.68,0:16:25.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.76,0:16:30.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不会吧这女孩愿意成为我的同伴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.48,0:16:36.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有其他愿意跟随尚文阁下的人了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.69,0:16:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.24,0:16:46.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文阁下之后请您自己招募喜欢的同伴补充人员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.54,0:16:48.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.29,0:16:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们每个月会给勇者们发放援助金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.00,0:16:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此次就给您比其他勇者更多的钱吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.50,0:17:02.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是安家费请收好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.88,0:17:05.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们给尚文大人准备了800枚银币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.43,0:17:08.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他勇者是600枚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.72,0:17:11.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用这笔钱凑齐装备踏上旅途吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.18,0:17:12.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.15,0:17:19.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见尚文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.86,0:17:23.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好保护她啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.57,0:17:27.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没法帮忙你要加油招募同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等时机到了再会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个盾之勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.54,0:17:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫麦茵·史菲雅今后承蒙您照顾了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:41.42,0:17:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是岩谷尚文请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.01,0:17:45.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.51,0:17:49.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平易近人的女孩子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.39,0:17:55.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她为了我成为了我的同伴一定要好好保护她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.85,0:18:00.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我们走吧那个麦茵小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.74,0:18:06.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先带您去城里转转
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.91,0:18:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天我也瞟了一眼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.08,0:18:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过近距离看更有异世界的感觉呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.71,0:18:18.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人您接下来打算怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.63,0:18:20.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯我想想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.25,0:18:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想先去卖武器和防具的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.72,0:18:29.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢有那么多钱的话可以买精良的装备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.60,0:18:32.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么我带您去我认识的好店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.85,0:18:34.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好这边走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.65,0:18:42.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可爱出门在外就得有一个女同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.61,0:18:48.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里就是我推荐的店
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.53,0:18:52.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是武器店吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.66,0:18:54.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.71,0:18:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人您第一次来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.62,0:19:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会进我们店里您眼光真独特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.29,0:19:02.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯是她介绍我来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘我们是不是在哪见过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.55,0:19:10.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以前也来过毕竟老板你的店很有名呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.01,0:19:12.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话让人听着高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来那边那位奇装异服的人是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.69,0:19:20.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板你能看出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.56,0:19:23.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你就是传说中的勇者大人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾代表你是不受期待的那个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.61,0:19:32.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我的事情传得那么快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了介意就输了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.41,0:19:40.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是盾之勇者岩谷尚文请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.29,0:19:42.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尚文啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.92,0:19:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了只要愿意常来光临不管是盾还是什么都无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.88,0:19:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多关照啊小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.93,0:19:54.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么老板能麻烦你给勇者大人挑选装备吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.39,0:19:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想大概250枚银币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.06,0:20:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从左边起是铁、魔法铁、魔法钢铁、银铁价格递增
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.07,0:20:07.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,性能有保证
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.90,0:20:10.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了这个我也能用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.57,0:20:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.62,0:20:13.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.50,0:20:20.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.33,0:20:21.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.17,0:20:24.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来好像突然被弹开了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.13,0:20:26.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.84,0:20:31.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁止事项?什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.39,0:20:35.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然要我光凭盾牌战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.26,0:20:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像因为这面盾的关系无法使用其他武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.73,0:20:42.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么原理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:45.98,0:20:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来就是一面小型盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.36,0:20:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿不下来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.36,0:20:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以换手拿但好像不能离开身体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.49,0:20:59.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能从这里感受到某种强大的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.91,0:21:02.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是用鉴定魔法也鉴定不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.29,0:21:06.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我算是见识到有趣的东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.38,0:21:08.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你要买防具吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.92,0:21:14.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像样点了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.43,0:21:16.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,价格大概多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.23,0:21:23.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优惠之后120枚银币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.94,0:21:25.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回收价多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.27,0:21:30.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想全新的二手那就用100枚银币收购
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.32,0:21:35.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者大人成长后就不需要这个了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.53,0:21:37.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我在问能卖多少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.70,0:21:39.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.70,0:21:41.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么要这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.58,0:21:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢惠顾我顺便送你一件内衬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.38,0:21:49.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去战斗吧勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.05,0:21:51.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.13,0:21:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提升等级吗终于要开始冒险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.24,0:23:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害可以无限吸收呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.96,0:23:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是传说武器的力量呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.71,0:23:16.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯被咬了都不痛应该也是多亏了它吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.30,0:23:21.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果想变形成新的盾似乎要吸收更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:22.18,0:23:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.10,0:23:27.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便问一句这个橙色气球怪的残骸可以卖吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.23,0:23:32.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以不过也就价值一枚铜币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.07,0:23:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看炼那边的情况这种魔物好像相当弱没办法吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:38.03,0:23:44.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让盾吸收的量满了之后等级提升它就会变化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.45,0:23:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天到此为止我们再去一趟武器店吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.33,0:23:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我买装备明天的成果会比今天更多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.84,0:23:56.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说得也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.88,0:23:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姑娘你的装备啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.80,0:24:03.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿上好装备的确能让你变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.85,0:24:05.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.14,0:24:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来价格也不会低我要趁现在砍价
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.06,0:24:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这勇者说话真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:13.31,0:24:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,减价八成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.57,0:24:16.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你蠢吗原价加两成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.61,0:24:18.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还加价了啊八成九分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.82,0:24:23.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不看货就砍价的家伙给双倍价就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:23.24,0:24:24.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.33,0:24:25.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,减价九成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:25.74,0:24:26.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加两成九分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:26.99,0:24:29.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以说别加价啊减价十成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:29.41,0:24:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这叫免费小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:31.33,0:24:32.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,免费送我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:35.13,0:24:37.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老板一共多少?减价六成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:37.88,0:24:42.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,优惠价480枚银币不能再少了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:42.13,0:24:45.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个这样一来还剩200枚银币吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:46.26,0:24:48.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵能不能稍微妥协一下?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.72,0:24:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不知道住宿和生活费要花多少呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:51.73,0:24:53.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:53.90,0:25:00.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我变强到时候能用打倒魔物获得的战利品卖钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:01.11,0:25:03.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是异世界召唤的王道剧情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:04.74,0:25:06.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你没办法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.20,0:25:09.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好老板麻烦你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:10.08,0:25:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢惠顾真是的你这勇者大人还挺会做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.88,0:25:16.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:17.25,0:25:20.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了老板哪里愿意回收这种残骸?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:21.59,0:25:26.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有回收魔物素材的店那边大部分东西都收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:26.68,0:25:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.60,0:25:30.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:30.98,0:25:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城里的料理的确美味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:33.10,0:25:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过还是这个更能让人体会到异世界的乐趣呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.61,0:25:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢慢品尝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:41.07,0:25:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天战斗的草原在这里吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:44.16,0:25:48.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的明天要去的是地图另一端拉法村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:48.99,0:25:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,穿过拉法村就有适合初学者的迷宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:53.50,0:25:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷宫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:54.67,0:25:59.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然不太适合赚钱但应该是个适合勇者大人练级的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:00.00,0:26:01.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:01.46,0:26:03.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装备也焕然一新
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:03.22,0:26:06.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有勇者大人的防御力在很轻松的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:06.55,0:26:09.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗谢谢很有价值的意见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:09.22,0:26:12.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不客气对了勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:13.48,0:26:15.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不喝红酒吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:17.56,0:26:19.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太喜欢酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:19.19,0:26:22.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗还挺好喝的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:27.99,0:26:31.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想和勇者大人一起喝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:34.37,0:26:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她好像突然变得很性感但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:38.25,0:26:40.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉我不喜欢酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:40.59,0:26:42.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗真可惜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:45.01,0:26:46.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:47.43,0:26:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:48.68,0:26:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的女性地位比较高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:50.76,0:26:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以没有男性会拒绝女性劝酒哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:55.43,0:26:58.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊我不太懂这些事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.48,0:27:00.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:01.61,0:27:04.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能定好之后的方针真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:05.15,0:27:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今晚想早点休息可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.45,0:27:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我要再喝一会儿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:12.24,0:27:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然独酌很寂寞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:14.79,0:27:16.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那那个麦茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:17.71,0:27:22.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你跟着我这完全不能战斗的盾之勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:23.59,0:27:25.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚的事我以后会想办法补偿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:27.97,0:27:31.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的晚安勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:32.22,0:27:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:39.48,0:27:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下200枚银币
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:41.81,0:27:44.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上30枚铜币的旅馆租两个房间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:45.28,0:27:48.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚餐每人5枚铜币两份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:48.53,0:27:51.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还剩199枚银币多一点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:53.87,0:27:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种行为正是来到外国旅游的日本人的行为呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:59.54,0:28:01.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天发生了好多事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:03.67,0:28:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打倒魔物原来是那种感觉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:07.42,0:28:10.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然今天只是在打气球一样的玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:10.76,0:28:14.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真的来到异世界了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:23.90,0:28:25.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,元康和树吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:29.07,0:28:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:30.74,0:28:32.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天还要早起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.25,0:28:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好该吃个饭启程了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:51.97,0:28:52.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:53.26,0:28:53.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:54.64,0:28:56.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,银币锁甲都不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:56.89,0:29:00.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我为了以防万一而拿着的便服也不见了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:00.56,0:29:03.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道在我睡着时被偷了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:11.45,0:29:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵不好了我们的钱和装备…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:16.37,0:29:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还在睡吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:17.83,0:29:19.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醒醒麦茵大事不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:21.12,0:29:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是城里的骑士吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:23.79,0:29:25.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正好听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:25.54,0:29:26.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是盾之勇者吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.38,0:29:28.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:29.63,0:29:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王下令召见你跟我们走一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:58.87,0:30:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:01.67,0:30:03.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:05.38,0:30:07.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵你没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:09.05,0:30:09.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:12.55,0:30:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,国王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:13.55,0:30:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我所有的财产和盾以外的装备都在睡觉的时候被偷走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:19.10,0:30:20.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请你抓住犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:20.60,0:30:21.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴邪恶之人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:22.23,0:30:23.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:24.57,0:30:26.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可怜的冒险者麦茵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:26.98,0:30:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真抱歉能麻烦你再作一次证吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:31.82,0:30:39.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者大人趁着醉酒突然闯进房间将我推倒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:40.33,0:30:46.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说「天还没亮呢」强行把我的衣服扯开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:47.76,0:30:49.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好不容易逃出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:50.05,0:30:55.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向住在同一个旅馆的元康大人求救
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:30:59.27,0:31:00.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:00.64,0:31:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是麦茵说最好等到早上再叫骑士我都要直接杀掉你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:06.48,0:31:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:07.94,0:31:11.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昨天吃完饭就在房间里睡觉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:11.57,0:31:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了就是那件锁甲趁夜偷东西的人是你吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:17.37,0:31:18.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁趁夜偷东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:19.16,0:31:23.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是昨天在酒馆遇到麦茵时她送我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:25.71,0:31:30.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者犯下了我国最不可饶恕的禁忌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:30.59,0:31:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禁忌?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:31.80,0:31:36.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在梅洛马格强奸女性未遂要被处以极刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:37.26,0:31:40.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不是你有勇者的身份立刻就会被处刑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:41.31,0:31:42.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处刑?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:43.10,0:31:46.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了这是误会啊我没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:47.06,0:31:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然那么肯定你拿出证据啊证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:52.15,0:31:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜查了盾之勇者的房间后那个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:56.53,0:31:58.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发现床上有这个东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:31:59.58,0:32:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:00.91,0:32:01.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,禽兽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:02.33,0:32:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是毫无疑问的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:04.50,0:32:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么啊我起床的时候可没有这东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:08.09,0:32:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜我开始还觉得事情有些奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:12.67,0:32:16.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你大概误以为勇者可以为所欲为吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:16.64,0:32:18.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有因为自己是勇者…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:19.39,0:32:24.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是这个异世界的主角搞清楚自己的斤两
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:27.94,0:32:29.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:30.61,0:32:31.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:32.44,0:32:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦茵麦茵你为什么要做这种事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:36.11,0:32:37.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是同伴吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:43.37,0:32:44.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:44.50,0:32:49.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「成为我的同伴」就是为此刻陷害我而撒下的彻头彻尾的谎言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:50.09,0:32:53.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我露出的笑脸展现的温柔全部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:32:56.05,0:33:01.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了我吧一开始就打算陷害我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:01.64,0:33:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕元康大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:03.68,0:33:05.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这个罪犯在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:05.77,0:33:09.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑你的目的就是我的钱和装备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:10.11,0:33:12.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两个串通好的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:13.78,0:33:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想想也是麦茵只称呼我为勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:19.16,0:33:21.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却直接叫元康的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:21.91,0:33:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果这都不叫证据那叫什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:25.62,0:33:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到他不仅嘴硬还信口胡言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:30.00,0:33:33.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢我也认为他不值得同情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:33.67,0:33:37.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然不该一次召唤四个人吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:38.18,0:33:41.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是如果没有召唤盾之勇者就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:41.85,0:33:44.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我们也没想到盾如此卑鄙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:44.10,0:33:46.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾又是盾吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:47.64,0:33:51.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为是盾因为不强就把我踢开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:51.73,0:33:55.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让事情发展尽可能对自己有利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:33:56.94,0:34:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好卑鄙这群人太卑鄙肮脏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:01.91,0:34:04.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个国家的其他人也根本不愿意相信我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:05.20,0:34:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种人有什么保护的必要?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:09.58,0:34:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以啊已经无所谓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:12.54,0:34:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上放我回原来的世界就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:15.34,0:34:18.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后要召唤新的盾之勇者还是召唤什么都随你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:18.72,0:34:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,异世界?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:20.22,0:34:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么来到异世界我还要遭这种罪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:23.76,0:34:27.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不顺心了就要逃吗太差劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:27.98,0:34:31.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不打算好好完成自己的职责吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:32.44,0:34:33.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚回去滚回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:33.86,0:34:36.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不想和强奸犯之流一起当勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:36.32,0:34:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:37.32,0:34:40.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来快把我送回原来的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:41.82,0:34:44.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒想顺了你的心意马上遣返你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:45.53,0:34:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但传说只有四圣勇者全部死亡时才能召唤新的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:53.04,0:34:54.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:54.17,0:34:55.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:55.79,0:34:57.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去我们回不去?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:34:58.71,0:35:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者将来袭的「浪潮」全部击退就能回到原本的世界吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:06.60,0:35:10.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们不得不和这家伙一起战斗吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:10.48,0:35:11.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:13.27,0:35:17.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就用自己的方式去处理浪潮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:18.57,0:35:19.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不许动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:19.61,0:35:21.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我闪开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:22.66,0:35:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:26.87,0:35:31.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们想干什么浪潮来袭前把我关在牢里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:31.66,0:35:34.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会把你关进去下一波浪潮不久就将来袭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:35.38,0:35:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再怎么说你也是唯一能对抗浪潮的勇者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:40.34,0:35:44.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我们已经将你的罪行告知国民这是惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:45.18,0:35:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后不要想在这个国家好好生存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:49.47,0:35:50.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:35:57.06,0:36:00.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就想要这个吧给你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:02.95,0:36:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂站住你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:07.20,0:36:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很弱的时间宝贵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:18.96,0:36:20.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:20.30,0:36:26.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我失去了信赖和金钱、名誉、身为勇者的尊严失去了一切
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:35.23,0:36:36.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿盾的小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:38.86,0:36:41.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了你把那个小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:41.73,0:36:43.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我打你一拳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:44.40,0:36:45.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:47.66,0:36:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:50.37,0:36:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛不是要揍我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:53.20,0:36:54.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不还是算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:54.96,0:36:56.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗你捡回一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:36:57.96,0:36:58.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:04.38,0:37:07.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这幅装扮会被人小瞧的这是点饯别礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:08.80,0:37:09.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多少钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:10.51,0:37:11.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:11.56,0:37:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这是处理品大概铜币5枚吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:15.06,0:37:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:17.40,0:37:18.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后我会来还的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:21.15,0:37:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可别死了小哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:37:55.68,0:37:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗一整夜总算有LV2了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:14.74,0:38:19.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想想这些东西1铜枚币收2个如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:20.17,0:38:22.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了你买下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:22.75,0:38:23.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:25.55,0:38:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感谢惠顾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:29.97,0:38:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:34.85,0:38:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,买下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:37.98,0:38:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,气球怪的气球吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:40.39,0:38:45.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,共20个呢1枚铜币收如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:46.82,0:38:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是对刚才那人说1铜枚币收2个吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:50.70,0:38:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:53.20,0:38:55.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟我们也要做生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:55.91,0:38:56.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:38:57.66,0:39:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么这家伙能卖得贵点吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:00.96,0:39:02.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟很有活力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:06.96,0:39:11.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也没叫你高价收购按照市场价来就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:11.72,0:39:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说你有讨厌我的理由吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:16.18,0:39:19.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我我明白了明白了拿掉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:20.77,0:39:22.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交涉成立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:22.60,0:39:25.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你不随便压价愿意成为我的常客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:25.90,0:39:27.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可以让你比市场价低一点收
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:29.11,0:39:32.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了虽然我很想拒绝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:32.99,0:39:36.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但收购的物品和钱是没有罪过的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:37.33,0:39:40.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有尽管把我的事情传出去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:41.29,0:39:45.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乱说话的商人会被咬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:45.46,0:39:47.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用你说我也会传的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:39:47.96,0:39:49.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今后请多关照
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:19.83,0:40:20.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:34.13,0:40:40.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说只要熟练运用哪怕变形成别的盾也能继承能力吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:42.35,0:40:43.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,叶型盾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:50.86,0:40:52.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太像游戏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:40:58.74,0:41:00.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,品质提高吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:06.37,0:41:09.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这药草不错在哪采到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:09.79,0:41:12.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离城不远的森林你不知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:14.63,0:41:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里居然能采到这么好的草药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:17.47,0:41:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为那里的药草品质要差点呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:28.02,0:41:30.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天起不管吃什么都没有味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:31.65,0:41:35.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盾之勇者大人我们做你的同伴吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:35.90,0:41:38.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对对感谢我们吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:40.87,0:41:44.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么先确认契约内容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:45.66,0:41:46.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:46.71,0:41:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先雇佣形式是计件发工资能明白什么意思吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:51.00,0:41:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不明白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:41:54.34,0:42:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冒险收入分配制我要拿大头最低四成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:02.97,0:42:05.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剩下的由我来分配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:06.43,0:42:09.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们什么都不做当然什么都分不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:10.23,0:42:14.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思这不就等于你可以全部独占嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:15.32,0:42:18.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好活跃就会分给你们如果你们能做出成果的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:20.74,0:42:23.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那赶紧去买装备吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:23.87,0:42:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,装备自费我没有义务帮你们买装备还培养你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:30.17,0:42:32.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了赶紧给钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:33.92,0:42:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上来就这么说也不用浪费时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:38.22,0:42:40.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么嘛还挺老实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:49.19,0:42:50.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:52.98,0:42:53.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:42:59.86,0:43:02.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,防御力强可攻击力不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:03.07,0:43:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不够所以无法打倒魔物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:05.62,0:43:07.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为无法打倒所以赚不到经验
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:08.66,0:43:12.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为赚不到经验所以攻击力永远上不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:13.04,0:43:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌的循环
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:15.09,0:43:15.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:22.47,0:43:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来您有烦恼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:30.18,0:43:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人手不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:32.56,0:43:34.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚好有您需要的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:35.31,0:43:37.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介绍同伴就不必了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:37.69,0:43:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴?不不我提供的可不是这种不方便的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:45.12,0:43:46.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:46.78,0:43:48.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您想知道吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:48.54,0:43:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别靠近我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:51.50,0:43:57.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有着我喜欢的眼神看来您和传闻中一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:57.42,0:43:59.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道我是谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:43:59.92,0:44:03.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然知道盾之勇者大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:03.63,0:44:07.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您有兴趣请随我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:20.19,0:44:21.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:23.86,0:44:27.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么你要给我提供作么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:28.53,0:44:32.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您看不明白吗是奴隶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:32.79,0:44:33.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:33.54,0:44:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯我是个奴隶商人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:38.71,0:44:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么认为我需要奴隶?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:41.67,0:44:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为奴隶绝不能撒谎绝不能背叛主人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:47.97,0:44:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奴隶身上会被施加重度诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:52.10,0:44:56.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以生命为代价以刻印为媒介的强力诅咒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:44:57.98,0:44:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:00.11,0:45:01.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:02.69,0:45:07.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您果然有成为好客人的潜质
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:10.70,0:45:12.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有不是人类的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:12.62,0:45:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些好歹还算人类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:15.67,0:45:19.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,详细和我说说毕竟我不熟悉这个世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:19.79,0:45:25.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚人是外貌与人类相似拥有与人类不同部位的人种的总称
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:25.80,0:45:29.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要当做仆人或用来从事体力劳动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:29.68,0:45:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓兽人是兽化程度高的亚人的称呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:34.39,0:45:39.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主要用于护卫或兽人战斗赌博中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:39.31,0:45:42.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此属于同一个分类吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:42.73,0:45:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯并且人们认为亚人更接近魔物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:47.57,0:45:50.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以在人类至上的国家生存困难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:45:51.24,0:45:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此被当做奴隶
